<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bubble Bubble</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: stretch;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .left-side {
            flex: 65%;
            background-color: #D8CEF6;
            padding: 50px;
        }
        .right-side {
            flex: 35%;
            padding: 50px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        form {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #555;
        }
        input[type="text"],
        input[type="password"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background-color: #E6E6E6;
            box-sizing: border-box;
	        border: none;
        }
	input[type="text"]:focus,
	input[type="password"]:focus {
    	    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    	    outline: none;
	}
        input[type="submit"] {
            background-color: #D8CEF6;
            color: #000000;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
	        margin: auto;
        }
        input[type="submit"]:hover {
            background-color: #bfb2e6;
        }
        .signup-btn {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .signup-btn a {
            color: #BCA9F5;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
	.usertype-label {
	    display: flex;
	    align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .usertype-label label {
        margin-right: 10px;
    }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="left-side">
            <h1>Bubble Bubble</h1>
	        <p>코인 빨래방 예약 서비스에 오신 것을 환영합니다.</p>
	        <p>로그인하여 예약하거나 회원가입하세요.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="right-side">
            <form action="login_process.php" method="post">
                <h2>로그인</h2>
		<div class="usertype-label">
		    <label>
                <input type="checkbox" name="usertype" value="일반회원">
                일반회원
		    </label>
		    <label>
                <input type="checkbox" name="usertype" value="관리자">
                관리자
		    </label>
		</div>
		<div>
            <label for="username">아이디</label>
            <input type="text" id="username" name="username" required>
		</div>
		<div>
		    <label for="password">비밀번호</label>
            <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required>
		</div>
		<input type="submit" value="로그인">
            </form>
            <div class="signup-btn">
                <p>계정이 없으신가요? <a href="subscribers/signup">회원가입</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

